input_query: What is the birth date of “Vice President of Engineering” ?
output_response: {'sql_query': "SELECT BirthDate FROM HumanResources.Employee WHERE JobTitle = 'Vice President of Engineering';"}

input_query: What department is the “Chief Executive Officer” part of?
output_response:
{'sql_query': "SELECT d.Name
FROM HumanResources.Employee AS e
JOIN HumanResources.EmployeeDepartmentHistory AS edh ON e.BusinessEntityID = edh.BusinessEntityID
JOIN HumanResources.Department AS d ON edh.DepartmentID = d.DepartmentID
WHERE e.JobTitle = 'Chief Executive Officer';"}
